---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const rows = [
  ['W A S D', 'Move'], ['MOUSE', 'Aim'], ['SHIFT', 'Sprint'],
  ['CTRL or C', 'Crouch (steadier aim)'], ['SPACE', 'Jump'],
  ['LEFT CLICK', 'Shoot'], ['RIGHT CLICK', 'AWP Sniper scope'],
  ['R', 'Reload'], ['1 / 2 / 3', 'AWP Sniper / Pistol / Knife'],
  ['Z / X / V', 'Voice commands (radio)'], ['TAB', 'Scoreboard'], ['ESC', 'Pause'],
];
---
<Layout title="How to play — Umain Arena">
  <h1>HOW TO PLAY</h1>
  <p>Open the <a href="/">game</a> in a desktop browser, set your nick, pick a team and a character, and hit PLAY.</p>

  <h2>Controls</h2>
  <table style="border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;max-width:520px">
    {rows.map(([k, a]) => (
      <tr>
        <td style="color:var(--yellow);padding:5px 14px 5px 0;font-family:Consolas,monospace;white-space:nowrap">{k}</td>
        <td style="color:#c9bfa4;padding:5px 0">{a}</td>
      </tr>
    ))}
  </table>

  <h2>Rules</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>4v4 matches (you + 3 allied bots vs 4 enemy bots), with a 2.5s respawn.</li>
    <li>Each round lasts 1:39. The team with more kills wins the round; 3 rounds win the match.</li>
    <li>The AWP Sniper is a one-shot kill; headshots have their own sound and marker. Multikills trigger Unreal Tournament-style announcements.</li>
    <li>Crouching (Ctrl or C) steadies your aim — essential for no-scope AWP shots.</li>
    <li>Your stats are saved in your browser (RANKING screen in the menu). Global ranking coming soon.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>The AWP Sniper is inaccurate without the scope: shoot while still and crouched, or use the scope (right click).</li>
    <li>The radar always shows allies, and shows enemies for 1.6s when they fire.</li>
    <li>The cover at the center is the best spot to hold mid.</li>
  </ul>
</Layout>
